    "attributes": {
        "action": "Give essential and key workers a tax break/refund.",
        "additional_details": "A one off gesture in recognition of those that have not had the benefit of being furloughed or given the opportunity to work from home.\r\nI speak specifically of those in the retail (supermarkets and the like), care home, and public health sectors.",
        "background": "Give all \"essential/key workers\" namely those who have worked continuously throughout the pandemic and can prove as much earning under \u00a328000 a full or partial refund of income tax paid from April 2020 to April 2021.",
